      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "To Glowishes Agentic OS αποτελεί ενα σύχρονο dashboard που θα μπορω να ελεγχο τους Agents για την\nδιαχειρηση του eshop μου (shopify) σε όλους του τομείς.         ",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "To Glowishes Agentic OS αποτελεί ενα σύχρονο dashboard που θα μπορω να ελεγχο τους Agents για την διαχειρηση του eshop μου (shopify) σε όλους του τομείς.         ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jTMTPwgb-SV6jGDVpgn6b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4840.801283041129,
      "y": 563.2064606696196,
      "width": 509.91937255859375,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f9a8d4",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b70",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 262518600,
      "version": 823,
      "versionNonce": 1122159416,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779134485250,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "L1 will be written by claude\nand will contain all the fixed \n\"instruction and more\" in order for \nClaude and Codex to be operational.\nMain purpose is to keep memory update\nminimize token usage. Make the reasearch\neasy in order to fullfill the taskes.\nKeep isntructions simply and to the point.\nMemory will be kept at obsidian and will be pumped out\nas prepocontition for skill, plugin, task.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "L1 will be written by claude\nand will contain all the fixed \n\"instruction and more\" in order for \nClaude and Codex to be operational.\nMain purpose is to keep memory update\nminimize token usage. Make the reasearch\neasy in order to fullfill the taskes.\nKeep isntructions simply and to the point.\nMemory will be kept at obsidian and will be pumped out\nas prepocontition for skill, plugin, task.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
